<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FaithBase - Stories That Inspire Faith</title>

<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background:#0b0f1a;
    color:white;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
    height:100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(11,15,26,1)),
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504052434569-70ad5836ab65');
    background-size:cover;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:4rem;
    color:#d4a017;
    margin:0;
    letter-spacing:2px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    max-width:700px;
    margin-top:15px;
    color:#ddd;
}

.btn{
    margin-top:25px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    background:#1f4e79;
    border:none;
    color:white;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:1rem;
    border-radius:5px;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#d4a017;
    color:black;
}

/* SECTION */
section{
    padding:60px 20px;
    max-width:1000px;
    margin:auto;
}

/* FEATURED */
.featured{
    background:#11182b;
    border-left:4px solid #d4a017;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:10px;
}

.featured h2{
    color:#d4a017;
}

/* SCRIPT BOX */
.script-box{
    background:#0f1626;
    padding:20px;
    margin-top:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    line-height:1.6;
}

.tag{
    display:inline-block;
    padding:5px 10px;
    background:#1f4e79;
    margin:5px;
    border-radius:5px;
    font-size:12px;
}

/* MODAL */
.modal{
    display:none;
    position:fixed;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    overflow:auto;
}

.modal-content{
    background:#11182b;
    margin:5% auto;
    padding:30px;
    width:90%;
    max-width:800px;
    border-radius:10px;
}

.close{
    float:right;
    cursor:pointer;
    color:red;
    font-size:25px;
}

.footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    background:#0b0f1a;
    color:#777;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
    <h1>FaithBase</h1>
    <p>Stories That Inspire Faith — Cinematic Christian Stage Plays & Biblical Dramas</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="openScript()">Watch Featured Script</button>
</div>

<!-- FEATURED -->
<section>
    <div class="featured">
        <h2>Featured Script</h2>
        <h1>14 Years: For What?</h1>

        <div>
            <span class="tag">5 Acts</span>
            <span class="tag">2–3 Hours</span>
            <span class="tag">~19 Characters</span>
            <span class="tag">Genesis Story</span>
        </div>

        <div class="script-box">
            A cinematic Christian stage play based on Jacob’s journey in 
            <b>Genesis</b>. A story of love, deception, waiting, brokenness, 
            and divine transformation.
            <br><br>
            Jacob works seven years for Rachel, only to be deceived into marrying Leah.
            He then works another seven years — questioning everything:
            <br><br>
            <i>"Fourteen years… for what?"</i>
        </div>

        <button class="btn" onclick="openScript()">Read Full Script</button>
        <button class="btn" onclick="alert('PDF download coming soon')">Download PDF</button>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section>
    <h2 style="color:#d4a017;">About FaithBase</h2>
    <p style="color:#ccc; line-height:1.7;">
        FaithBase is a cinematic Christian storytelling platform created to bring 
        Bible stories to life through stage plays, drama scripts, and creative storytelling.
        <br><br>
        Built by Emmanuel Mbiru.
    </p>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
    © 2026 FaithBase | Stories That Inspire Faith
</div>

<!-- MODAL -->
<div id="modal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close" onclick="closeScript()">&times;</span>

        <h1 style="color:#d4a017;">14 Years: For What?</h1>

        <p><b>Act Structure:</b></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Act 1: Love & Promise</li>
            <li>Act 2: Betrayal</li>
            <li>Act 3: The Cost</li>
            <li>Act 4: The Sons</li>
            <li>Act 5: Peniel</li>
        </ul>

        <hr>

        <p style="line-height:1.8;">
        Jacob’s journey begins with love but is shaped by deception.
        He works fourteen years for Rachel, only to discover that waiting
        is not punishment — it is transformation.
        <br><br>
        In the end, he does not just get Rachel…
        <br>
        <b>He becomes Israel.</b>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
function openScript(){
    document.getElementById("modal").style.display = "block";
}

function closeScript(){
    document.getElementById("modal").style.display = "none";
}

window.onclick = function(event){
    let modal = document.getElementById("modal");
    if(event.target == modal){
        modal.style.display = "none";
    }
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
